\begin_inset Formula $QTQ^{*}QT^{*}Q^{*}=QT^{*}Q^{*}QTQ^{*}$
\end_inset

 and hence (cancelling the 
\begin_inset Formula $Q$
\end_inset

s) 
\begin_inset Formula $TT^{*}=T^{*}T$
\end_inset

.
\begin_inset Newline newline
\end_inset


\begin_inset Newline newline
\end_inset

The (1,1) entry of 
\begin_inset Formula $T^{*}T$
\end_inset

